<item>
            <title>[LU-3039] OI scrub and LFSCK do not work on lustre-2.4</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-3039</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;1. Some patches landed to Lustre-2.4 recently break OI scrub and LFSCK.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;2. There is deadlock between LFSCK engine and OI scrub thread. We found the LFSCK cannot finish as expected when we test large file set (more than 10M files).&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;All these issues should be resolved before Lustre-2.4 deadline.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
